p durch die Komplexität der Paradoxie, die unsere Vorstellungen herausfordert.  aHow can the now be imagined if it refuses to be grasped? A fascinating journey through time to the 'Long Now Foundation', where this paradox became a part of the Californian hippie and media culture.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aCivilizationxHistory. 0aComplexity. 0aContemporary. 0aCounterculture. 0aCultural Studies. 0aDas Lange Jetzt. 0aErinnerungskultur. 0aGegenkultur. 0aGegenwart. 0aKalifornien. 0aKomplexität. 0aKulturgeschichte. 0aKulturwissenschaft. 0aMedia Aesthetics. 0aMedia Culture Studies. 0aMedia Philosophy. 0aMedia. 0aMedien. 0aMedienästhetik. 0aMedienphilosophie. 0aMemory Culture. 0aParadox. 0aParadoxie. 0aPhilosophie. 0aPhilosophy. 0aSilicon Valley. 0aThe Long Now Foundation. 0aThe Long Now. 4aDas Lange Jetzt. 4aErinnerungskultur. 4aGegenkultur. 4aGegenwart. 4aKalifornien. 4aKomplexität. 4aKulturgeschichte. 4aKulturwissenschaft. 4aMedien. 4aMedienphilosophie. 4aMedienästhetik. 4aParadoxie. 4aPhilosophie. 4aSilicon Valley. 4aThe Long Now Foundation. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Media Studies.2bisacsh  aCalifornia.  aComplexity.  aContemporary.  aCounter-culture.  aCultural History.  aCultural Studies.  aMedia Aesthetics.  aMedia Philosophy.  aMedia.  aMemory Culture.  aParadox.  aPhilosophy.  aSilicon Valley.  aThe Long Now Foundation.  aThe Long Now.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2017z978311071954308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2017z9783110540550oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2017z9783110547764oZDB-23-DEG40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839437285zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de 